snippet.title: My Current December Beauty Favorites | Holiday 2020 | Sincerely Amber Marie Mack
snippet.description:
My Current December Makeup Beauty Favorites Fall/Holiday 2020
#fallmakeup #fall2020 #holiday2020 #woc #favorites #currentbeautyfavorites

Welcome back to my channel! In todays video, I just wanted to sit and chant with you guys about all my current favorite products I have been using and loving for the last couple of months! Let me know if you guys enjoy videos like this! && let me know in the comments what other videos you would like to see on my channel! Thanks for watching and don’t forget to LIKE, SUBSCRIBE, SHARE, and COMMENT! See you in my next video! 

Products mentioned:
Milk Hydro Grip Primer 
Maybelline Camo Color Corrector- orange 
ELF Hydrating Camo Concealer- Deep Chestnut 
Fenty Brow MVP
Anastasia Beverly Hills Brow Powder Duo
Dermablend Loose Powder- Warm Saffron
Fenty Beauty Loose Powder- Cashew 
Huda Beauty Stick Foundation 
Nars Soft Matte Foundation 
Colourpop Pretty Fresh Concealer 
Fenty Beauty What it Dew Hydrating Mist
Sephora Microsmooth Bakes Powder
Makeup Revolution Splendor Matte Bronzer- Deep 
Sephora Pro face Palette- Deep
Nyx Ultimate Utopia Eyeshadow Palette 
Kiss Lashes- #11
Fenty Beauty Mascara 
Maybelline Lifter Gloss- Amber
Juvias Place Lip Liner- Kola
NYX Soft Matte Lip Cream- London 
Charlotte Tilbury Setting Spray
